        },
        {
            "text": "No excess of events was observed, therefore a lower limit on the 0\u03bd\u03b2 \u03b2 half-life was obtained, T   mass, m \u03b2 \u03b2 < 0.6 \u2212 1.3 eV, according to the most recent NME calculations [4,5,6,7]. ",
