        },
        {
            "text": "From the 100 Mo half-life limit shown in Table 2, a limit was obtained of \u03b7 11 (q)LR < 9.2 \u00d7 10 \u22129 that corresponds to upper limits on the trilinear couplings of \u03bb 111 \u03bb 111 < 1.7 \u00d7 10 \u22125 , \u03bb 112 \u03bb 121 < 8.7 \u00d7 10 \u22127 and \u03bb 113 \u03bb 131 < 3.6 \u00d7 10 \u22128 [10].",
